org.cyclops.cyclopscore.ingredient.collection

Interface IIngredientListMutable<T,M>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The instance type.
    M - The matching condition parameter.
    All Superinterfaces:
    IIngredientCollection<T,M>, IIngredientCollectionLike<T,M,T>, IIngredientCollectionMutable<T,M>, IIngredientList<T,M>, java.lang.Iterable<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    IngredientArrayList, IngredientLinkedList, IngredientList

    public interface IIngredientListMutable<T,M>
extends IIngredientList<T,M>, IIngredientCollectionMutable<T,M>
    A mutable ingredient collection using list semantics. This means that instances exist in a predefined order and that instances can exist multiple time in the collection.
    See Also:
    List
